Fetch Wikipedia access data

Source: R/endpoints.R
wiki.Rd

API docs: https://cmu-delphi.github.io/delphi-epidata/api/wiki.html

wiki(articles, dates = NULL, epiweeks = NULL, hours = NULL, language = "en")

Arguments

articles

character vector. The articles to fetch.

dates

timeset. The dates to fetch. Mutually exclusive with epiweeks.

epiweeks

timeset. The epiweeks to fetch. Mutually exclusive with dates.

hours

integer. Optionally, the hours to fetch.

language

string. The language to fetch.

Value

epidata_call

Examples

# \donttest{
wiki(articles = "avian_influenza", epiweeks = epirange(201501, 201601)) %>% fetch()
